Example Single-Cell RNA-Seq Counts

Source: R/data.R
single_cell_counts.Rd

Modified version of scater::sc_example_counts, with dimnames formatted in camel case for package consistency.

single_cell_counts

Format

An object of class dgCMatrix with 1000 rows and 40 columns.

Examples

summary(single_cell_counts)
